description: Milestone edition of #LOSP!!! Ross Levitan and Brandon Piller share their fondest memories and give thanks before turning our attention to this Ottawa Senators Game Day. (Also, do the Sens have a new emergency goalie??). We provide injury and line updates from this mornings skate, dissect what will be a tough match-up against the dangerous Minnesota Wild and give stick taps to Tyler Boucher for scoring his first OHL goal with the Ottawa 67s!
